{
 "name": "RPlog_Reunion_with_the_Princess",
 "title": "Reunion with the Princess",
 "summary": "On the golden beaches of Coronet City on Corellia, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios reunites with Luke Skywalker, Han Solo, and the Princess Leia Organa Solo, with the dark adept Simon Sezirok also drawn into the gathering. Against the majestic sweep of sea and gold sand, old friends and family reconnect, the warmth of reunion mingling with the undercurrents of tension that Simon's presence brings. The seaside meeting weaves together the threads of the Jedi's relationships with the heroes of the Rebellion.",
